(194, 1, '2015-08-07 10:29:55', '2015-08-07 08:29:55', '[one_half last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\r\n<h2>BEML - Serie</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Niederspannungsmaschinen</li>\r\n	<li>Leistung: 400V, 480V, 690V</li>\r\n	<li>Ampere: 600 – 6.000 kVA</li>\r\n	<li>Umdrehung: 500 – 1800 U/min</li>\r\n	<li>4 - 12 Pole pro Maschiene</li>\r\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\r\n<h3>Product Range</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-132\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/bem-produktbilder-02.png\" alt=\"bem-produktbilder-02\" width=\"640\" height=\"204\" />[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\r\n<h3>Eigenschaften</h3>\r\nBEMPower® Produkte werde nach folgenden Kriterien entwickelt und produziert:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IEC / EN 60034</li>\r\n	<li>BS5000</li>\r\n	<li>VDE 0530</li>\r\n	<li>ISO 8528-9</li>\r\n	<li>Schiffsklassifikationsgesellschaft: ABS / BV / CCS / DNV</li>\r\n	<li>auf Kundenwunsch: UL / CSA / NEMA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\r\n<h3>Schutzarten</h3>\r\n<span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"hps\">Mindestanforderung bei elektrischen Maschinen ist IP23</span> <span class=\"hps\">/</span> <span class=\"hps\">IC01</span></span> (tropfwassergeschütztes Gehäuse)\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Alternative Optionen für Gehäuse und Kühlung</strong></span>\r\n<h4>Gehäuse Optionen  (IEC60034-5)</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP43 - Ausstattung mit Filtern</li>\r\n	<li>IP44/IP54 -<span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"hps\"> Geschlossene</span> <span class=\"hps\">Luft/Luft</span> <span class=\"hps\">oder Luft/</span><span class=\"hps\">Wasser - Wärmetauscher</span> <span class=\"hps\">mit</span> <span class=\"hps\">Leckageerkennung</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Kühlungs Optionen (IEC60034-6)</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IC11 - gleiteter Lufteinlass</li>\r\n	<li>IC21 - geleiteter Luftauslass</li>\r\n	<li>IC31 - geleiteter Lufteinlass und Luftauslass</li>\r\n	<li>IC616/611 - <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"short_text\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"hps\">Luft/</span><span class=\"hps\">Luft - Wärmetauscher</span></span></li>\r\n	<li>IC81W - <span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"de\"><span class=\"hps\">Luft/</span><span class=\"hps\">Wasser - Wärmetauscher</span> <span class=\"hps\">mit</span> <span class=\"hps\">Leckageerkennung</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\r\n<h2>BEMH - Serie</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hochspannungsmaschinen</li>\r\n	<li>Leistung: 3.000 V - 15.000 V</li>\r\n	<li>Ampere: 0,5 MVA – 30 MVA</li>\r\n	<li>Umdrehung: 500 – 1800 U/min</li>\r\n	<li>4 - 14 Pole pro Maschiene</li>\r\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\r\n<h3>Product Range</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-133\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/bem-produktbilder-01.png\" alt=\"bem-produktbilder-01\" width=\"640\" height=\"204\" />[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\r\n<h3>Eigenschaften</h3>\r\nBEMPower® Produkte werde nach folgenden Kriterien entwickelt und produziert:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IEC / EN 60034</li>\r\n	<li>BS5000</li>\r\n	<li>VDE 0530</li>\r\n	<li>ISO 8528-9</li>\r\n	<li>Schiffsklassifikationsgesellschaft: ABS / BV / CCS / DNV</li>\r\n	<li>auf Kun