(240, 1, '2015-08-10 07:06:38', '2015-08-10 05:06:38', '<h1>Data Privacy Declaration</h1>\r\n<strong>Data Privacy Declaration for Website www.bem-power.de</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Collection, Processing and Use of Person-Related Data (“Personal Data”)</strong>\r\nInsofar as personal or business data (e-mail addresses, names, postal addresses) can be entered by the user in this website, disclosure is on an expressly voluntary basis.\r\n\r\nWhen registering for our newsletter, you inform us of your e‑mail address and optionally of other data too. We use this information solely for the purpose of sending you the newslater. We continue to store the data you entered when registering for the newsletter until you cancel your registration for the newsletter. You can cancel your registration at any time by using the link provided in the newsletter or by notifying us accordingly. By cancelling, you object to further use of your e‑mail address.\r\n\r\n<strong>Use of Own Cookies</strong>\r\nThis website uses its own cookies to increase usability. (Cookies are data records which are sent by the web server to the user’s browser and stored there for use by a subsequent invocation.) No personal data of any kind is stored in our own cookies. You can prevent the use of cookies in general if you prohibit storage of cookies by means of a setting in your browser.\r\n\r\n<strong>Further Information and Contacts</strong>\r\nPlease contact us if you have any questions about this data privacy declaration. You can ask at any time whether and which data of yours is stored in our systems. In addition, you can send us information, requests for deletions and corrections..', 'privacy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-10 07:06:38', '2015-08-10 05:06:38', '', 72, 'http://127.0.0.1/bem/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
